title: Come home with confidence.🏡🔑
posting_body: ['Sunchase Apartments is a welcoming, quiet apartment community conveniently located off of Highway 79 and close to IH-35.', 'We are just a moment’s drive away from shops, dining, entertainment, and schools.', 'Enjoy a day of shopping at the Round Rock Premium Outlet Mall or swing by Dell Diamond to catch a game or two.', 'Students will have easy access to surrounding Round Rock ISD schools as well as multiple college campuses.', 'Texas State University, Texas A&M Health Science Center, and Austin Community College R.R. are all less than five miles from property.', 'We are pet friendly and would love to have you and your furry critters.', 'We have NO breed or weight restrictions.', 'Sunchase Apartments is your one and only place for comfortable, easy living!', 'All we are missing is you!', 'SUNCHASE APARTMENTS', '1200 Sunrise Road –', 'Round Rock, TX 78664', '---------------------------', '---------------------------', 'Property Details:', '2 BEDROOM | 1 BATHROOM', '***Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed***', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Lease Terms:', '• $1,320.00/Month', '• $200.00 Deposit', '• Lease Length: 1 YEAR', 'Unit Amenities:', '• Dishwasher', '• Garbage Disposal', '• Stove', '• Refrigerator', 'Building Amenities:', '• Cable Ready', '• Near Parks', '• On Site Laundry', '• Swimming Pool', '•', 'Wired For Internet', 'Call Christa (not a locator)', 'show contact info', 'to get more information!']
